# BOS API

## LOCAL

  - new<P> -> Self
  - run<C> -> Result<Call, E>

  - session
    - connection
    - config
    - cache
    - live


## session

  - open
  - close
  - stat

## live

  - subscribe(SubscriptionParams) -> Result<Subscriptions, E>
  - unsubscribe(SubscriptionParams) -> Result<Subscriptions, E>
  - post(Message) -> Result<Call, E>
  - register(Message, Handler)
  - handle(Message) -> Result<Call, E>

## resources

### read

  - list<P> -> Result<TagListings, E>
  - search<P> -> Result<SearchResults, E>
  - stream<T, P> -> ??
  - read<T, P> -> Result<T, E>
  - refresh<T> -> Result<T, E>

Generic reader (server):
  - build
  - auth
  - render


Generic streamer (server):
  - build
  - auth
  - stream

### write

  - create<T, P> -> Result<T, E>
  - update<T, P> -> Result<T, E>
  - delete<T, P> -> Result<T, E>
  - stream<T, P> -> ??

Generic writer (server):

  - build
  - auth
  - validate
  - commit
  - render

Other:
  - stream (wraps change/validate/commit loop)
  - open_transaction
  - close_transaction


## blts

### blocks

  - insert
  - update
  - upsert
  - tagsert
  - delete
  - link
  - unlink

### tags

  - insert
  - update
  - upsert
  - move
  - delete
  - share
  - unshare

### public

  - import
  - sync
  - export
  - purge
